      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m selling my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it\u2019s like stepping back in time to the day it was first bought! It\u2019s been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged, meticulously cleaned, and it drives like an absolute dream. No scratches, no dents, just pure perfection. I'm really sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to fall in love with it just like I did. Come check it out and see for yourself!",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
