      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 41
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is an exceptional specimen of high-revving, naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS variable valve timing, delivering a seamless power delivery up to its 8,000 RPM redline. The Getrag 6-speed manual transmission provides tactile, short-throw shifts, sending power to the rear wheels through a variable M-differential lock. Crucially, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the rod bearings have been serviced\u2014addressing the primary mechanical concerns of this chassis. The suspension retains its factory-spec damping and lateral rigidity, while the exterior finish shows no signs of clear coat failure or panel gap deviation. This is a turn-key, investment-grade vehicle for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
